value.labelText: What do startups need to know?

value.text: A tech startup is a startup that is focused on technology-based products or services. Due to the nature of our modern world and the involvement of technology most startups are thought of as tech startups. However, technology on its own is not a defining factor of a startup; innovation and novelty are.
